DESCRIPTION: Core implementation of a data table component with sorting, filtering, pagination, and row selection functionality using React and useReactTable hook.
SOURCE: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/design-system/content/docs/components/data-table.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_15

