TITLE: Implementing heartbeat mechanism for libcluster Postgres strategy
DESCRIPTION: Elixir code for the heartbeat mechanism that periodically notifies other nodes of its existence. This is crucial for maintaining the cluster and enabling self-healing capabilities.
SOURCE: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/www/_blog/2024-01-09-elixir-clustering-using-postgres.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: elixir
CODE:
```
# lib/cluster/strategy/postgres.ex:73
def handle_info(:heartbeat, state) do
    Process.cancel_timer(state.meta.heartbeat_ref)
    Postgrex.query(state.meta.conn, "NOTIFY #{state.config[:channel_name]}, '#{node()}'", [])
    ref = heartbeat(state.config[:heartbeat_interval])
    {:noreply, put_in(state.meta.heartbeat_ref, ref)}
end
```

