TITLE: Implementing Base Synchronized Object Class in Dart
DESCRIPTION: Abstract base class for objects that need real-time synchronization, including factory method for JSON parsing.
SOURCE: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/www/_blog/2024-01-26-flutter-figma-clone.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: dart
CODE:
```
abstract class SyncedObject {
  /// UUID unique identifier of the object
  final String id;

  factory SyncedObject.fromJson(Map<String, dynamic> json) {
    final objectType = json['object_type'];
    if (objectType == UserCursor.type) {
      return UserCursor.fromJson(json);
    } else {
      return CanvasObject.fromJson(json);
    }
  }

  SyncedObject({
    required this.id,
  });

  Map<String, dynamic> toJson();
}
```

