CODE:
```
select
  cf_connecting_ip
from
  edge_logs
-- Unpack 'metadata' field
cross join unnest(metadata) AS metadata
-- unpack 'request' from 'metadata'
cross join unnest(request) AS request;
-- unpack 'headers' from 'request'
cross join unnest(headers) AS headers;
```

