TITLE: Creating a Figure-8 Animation Pattern in React Three Fiber
DESCRIPTION: This code creates a figure-8 animation pattern by alternating the sign of the cosine function based on whether the current loop count is even or odd.
SOURCE: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/www/_blog/2023-08-04-interactive-constellation-threejs-react-three-fiber.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
const isEven = Math.floor(timer / circumference) % 2 == 0

particle.current.position.x = Math.sin(timer) * widthRadius
particle.current.position.y = isEven
  ? Math.cos(timer) * heightRadius - heightRadius
  : -Math.cos(timer) * heightRadius + heightRadius
```

