TITLE: Fetching Movie Data from TMDB API
DESCRIPTION: Queries the TMDB API to retrieve popular movies for a specific year with various filters and parameters.
SOURCE: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/www/_blog/2024-02-26-content-recommendation-with-flutter.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_1

