DESCRIPTION: Basic implementation of a text confirm dialog with icon, title 'Heads up!' and description about adding components using CLI.
SOURCE: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/design-system/content/docs/fragments/text-confirm-dialog.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
<ComponentPreview
  name="text-confirm-dialog-demo"
  description="An alert with an icon, title and description. The title says 'Heads up!' and the description is 'You can add components to your app using the cli.'"
  peekCode
  showDottedGrid
  wide
/>
```

