TITLE: Carousel with Fixed Item Sizes
DESCRIPTION: Example of setting fixed sizes for carousel items using utility classes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/design-system/content/docs/components/carousel.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
// 33% of the carousel width.
<Carousel>
  <CarouselContent>
    <CarouselItem className="basis-1/3">...</CarouselItem>
    <CarouselItem className="basis-1/3">...</CarouselItem>
    <CarouselItem className="basis-1/3">...</CarouselItem>
  </CarouselContent>
</Carousel>
```

