TITLE: TailwindCSS Background and Foreground Class Mappings
DESCRIPTION: Examples of how Figma variable names are mapped to TailwindCSS utility classes for background and foreground (text) colors.
SOURCE: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/www/_blog/2023-12-08-how-design-works-at-supabase.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: css
CODE:
```
background.default -> bg
background.alternative -> bg-alternative
foreground.DEFAULT -> text
foreground.light -> text-light
```

