TITLE: Importing Card Components
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to import all necessary card-related components from the UI library
SOURCE: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/design-system/content/docs/components/card.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import {
  Card,
  CardContent,
  CardDescription,
  CardFooter,
  CardHeader,
  CardTitle,
} from '@/components/ui/card'
```

