TITLE: Installing Radio Group Dependencies Manually
DESCRIPTION: Command to install the required dependency for the Radio Group component using npm.
SOURCE: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/design-system/content/docs/components/radio-group.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
npm install @radix-ui/react-radio-group
```

